Uttar Pradesh UPSESSB UP Post Graduate Teacher PGT Online Form 2022 for 624 Post

Short Information : Uttar Pradesh Secondary Education Service Selection Board (UPSESSB) has released the notification of Post Graduate Teacher PGT Teacher Recruitment for 624 posts. Those who are interested in this recruitment and fulfill the eligibility can apply online from 09 June 2022 to 03 July 2022. For the information of eligibility, age limit, selection procedure, pay scale, syllabus in recruitment, read the notification and then apply.
